text: One Logan Square is a high-rise building located in the Logan Square neighborhood of Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. The building stands at 400 ft (122 m) with 31 floors, and was completed in 1983. It is currently the 31st-tallest building in Philadelphia. The architectural firm responsible for the building's design is Kohn Pedersen Fox Associates PC. ==See also== * List of tallest buildings in Philadelphia * Buildings and architecture of Philadelphia ==References== ==External links== * Emporis * SkyscraperPage Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Philadelphia Category:Kohn Pedersen Fox buildings Category:Office buildings completed in 1983
